<p><div align="center"><table width="50%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>
<td width="150"><br></td>
<td align="center"><b>
<i>Andrena nigrihirta</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">(Ashmead, 1890)</font></b><br>
<small><i>Cilissa nigrihirta </i>Ashmead, 1890; <i>Andrena longihirtiscopa </i>Viereck, 1904; <i>Andrena decussata </i>Viereck, 1904; <i>Andrena decussatula </i>Viereck, 1904; <i>Andrena synthiridis </i>Cockerell, 1906; <i>Andrena novae-angliae </i>Viereck, 1907; <i>Andrena novaeangliae </i>Viereck, 1907; <i>Andrena nivaloides </i>Graenicher, 1911; <i>Andrena &#40;Andrena&#41; discolor </i>Viereck, 1916; <i>Andrena &#40;Andrena&#41; tumida </i>Viereck, 1922; <i>Andrena &#40;Andrena&#41; vancouverensis </i>Viereck, 1924; <i>Andrena &#40;Andrena&#41; nigrovaria </i>Viereck, 1924; <i>Andrena &#40;Andrena&#41; marina </i>Viereck, 1926; <i>Andrena ripariella </i>Cockerell, 1936; <i>Andrena &#40;Thysandrena&#41; crenata </i>Mitchell, 1960; <i>Andrena &#40;Euandrena&#41; nigrihirta </i>&#40;Ashmead, 1890&#41;</small><p>
